rees and game-changing effects. Choose carefully, as you can only pick one upgrade each stage from a selection of 3 randomly presented options.  Be a fire mage destroying everything in your path with massive AOEs, burning damage and multiple projectiles. Or master lightning, shocking your enemies making them vulnerable to your melee attacks. Or take advantage of frost and cold, whizzing in and out of combat applying chill and freeze effects slowing your enemies in their tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406370/extras/7866193c3631e8ff16a481285faf1f56.poster.avif?t=1761234956\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406370/extras/7866193c3631e8ff16a481285faf1f56.webm?t=1761234956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406370/extras/7866193c3631e8ff16a481285faf1f56.mp4?t=1761234956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmospheric dark-fantasy locations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack and slash enemies in beautifully hand-crafted locations with randomized layouts on each run. Explore dark dungeons filled with aggressive skeletons, abandoned medieval villages, derelict cathedral libraries and courtyards, or gloomy and ominous cemeteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Persistent character progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is not the end. Gain experience the longer you stay alive and improve your character after each playthrough with various perks from the talent tree making you more powerful and more prepared to progress further and further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique enemies and bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_p